section 3 A

exp_1 = expression(x^2)
my_deriv_1 = D(exp_1, "x")
my_deriv_1
## 2 * x
x <- 3
eval(my_deriv_1)
## [1] 6

section 3 B

ex_2 = expression(2 * (3 * a + 2)^4 -5)
my_deriv_2 = D(ex_2, "a")
my_deriv_2
## 2 * (4 * (3 * (3 * a + 2)^3))
a <- 1.2
eval(my_deriv_2)
## [1] 4214.784

Section 3 C

ex_3 = expression((-4 * t)/(t^2 + 1)^3)
my_deriv_3 = D(ex_3, "t")
my_deriv_3
## -(4/(t^2 + 1)^3 + (-4 * t) * (3 * (2 * t * (t^2 + 1)^2))/((t^2 + 
##     1)^3)^2)
t <- 0
eval(my_deriv_3)
## [1] -4
